document_data.mainbody:
Coachlamp Lane was a road that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Coachlamp Lane was located in the southern section of Waterdeeps Southern Ward. The road originated on the southern end of the High Road where it branched east, crossed Carters Way, then turned southeast to end within a neighborhood at a deadend.
Hlakken Stables and Tehmaks Coaches were both located along Coachlamp Lane.
